author: ogel3001
title: A bad set for its price.
review:
This set is not worth what you would have to pay for it.

Pros

  • Rare Axel fig.
  • Rare dark turquoise colors.

Cons

  • The vehicle is small and has nothing to indicate that it flies.
  • The sweets were made in 2000. Hmm.

Overall, I would not get this set unless you see it at a cheap price.
